<h1><b>JustChess.org</b></h1>

<div class="about-page">
  <p><b>A multiplayer chess server started in 2024 by <a href="https://github.com/treepeck">Artem Bielikov</a></b></p>

  <h3>Features:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Match history</li>
    <li>Glicko-2 rating system</li>
    <li>Skill-based matchmaking</li>
    <li>Multiple concurrent games</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Under development:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>AI analysis of games on demand</li>
  </ul>

